name: Blue and green tortoises
description: The tortoises first started appearing when the canvas expanded for the penultimate time. The german community from r/placeDE, helding the flag behind the tortoises, first decided to keep them. The tortoises were replaced by one of the last artworks of the r/placeDE community, the "Geschwister Scholl". However, some tortoises on the very left of the flag made it to the final canvas.
